course_title: Clinical Methods in Psychoanalysis: Freud I
class_notes:
TOPIC: Freud I
Course originates in the Emory University Psychoanalytic Institute (EUPI) and will meet at EUPI in Executive Park #6.  This course will cover the writings of Sigmund Freud from his earliest analytic writings (1893) up through the cases of the Rat Man, Little Hans, and Dr. Schreber (1911). Freud II will be offered in Spring 2024.
